<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Devices on memoria digital</title><link>https://volteret4.github.io/notas/tags/devices/</link><description>Recent content in Devices on memoria digital</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>es-es</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 31 Jul 2025 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://volteret4.github.io/notas/tags/devices/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Detectar Dispositivos Bluetooth</title><link>https://volteret4.github.io/notas/p/detectar-dispositivos-bluetooth/</link><pubDate>Thu, 31 Jul 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://volteret4.github.io/notas/p/detectar-dispositivos-bluetooth/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://stackoverflow.com/questions/73615751/how-to-detect-and-enable-a-bluetooth-adapter" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Origen&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;El kernel de Linux registrará todos los dispositivos conectados a él durante el inicio y puede encontrarlos con el siguiente commando.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;div class="chroma"&gt;
&lt;table class="lntable"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="lntd"&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class="lntd"&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;dmesg &lt;span class="p"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; grep -i blue
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Puedes usar &lt;code&gt;bluetoothctl&lt;/code&gt; para arrancar la app y luego usar:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;div class="chroma"&gt;
&lt;table class="lntable"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="lntd"&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;2
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;3
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;4
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;5
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class="lntd"&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;power on
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;agent on
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;scan on
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;connect MAC_ADDRESS
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;trust MAC_ADDRESS
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>